			<div id="body-content">

			<h1 class="entry-title">Does net neutrality really matter?</h1>

					

				

				<h2 class="subhead">Competition, access to bandwidth, and other issues muddy the net neutrality waters.</h2>

			
			

			<div class="entry-meta">				

				
					<span class="meta-sep">by</span> 	

					
						<span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" rel="author" href="http://radar.oreilly.com/andyo" title="View all posts by Andy Oram">

						Andy Oram</a></span> |								

					
				<!-- RSPEAK_STOP -->

				
					<a href="http://twitter.com/praxagora"> @praxagora</a> |

				
				
					<a href="https://plus.google.com/#111030861447662731288/posts"> +Andy Oram</a> |

				
				
				
					<span class="comments-link utility-items"><a href="http://radar.oreilly.com/2014/08/does-net-neutrality-really-matter.html#comments" title="Comment on Does net neutrality really matter?"><span class="dsq-postid" rel="70161 http://radar.oreilly.com/?p=70161">Comments: 32</span></a></span>

					<span class="meta-sep utility-items"> | </span>

					

				
				<span class="entry-date">August 15, 2014</span> 				

			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->

			

			<div class="entry-utility social">						

